Wade HOLMAN, Jr., Appellant, v. Robert L. EKLUND, Appellee. No. 20181. United States Court of Appeals Ninth Circuit. Jan. 31, 1966. Rehearing Denied March 11, 1966. Wade Holman, Jr., in pro. per. Thomas C. Lynch, Atty. Gen., of Cal., William E. James, Asst. Atty. Gen.; Anthony M. Summers, Deputy Atty. Gen., Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before BARNES, JERTBERG and ELY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM:

The order appealed from is affirmed.
